prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon-style sloth wearing a tiny, lopsided party hat, hanging upside down from a tree branch that is bending slightly under its weight. The sloth has a wide, lazy, blissfully happy smile on its face and is slowly reaching one paw towards a single cupcake with a lit candle, which is precariously balanced on another branch just out of reach. The greeting "happy birthday" is written in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script in the center of the card. The entire scene is a flat 2D watercolor painting, with soft, flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture background, and organic paint bleeds around the edges of the sloth and leaves.
